03:26:06.005 --> 03:26:08.013
and two that have been untouched.

03:26:08.013 --> 03:26:09.650
TRAVIS: Oh, the song broke, it didn't die.

03:26:09.650 --> 03:26:11.658
LIAM: 16 wisdom save.

03:26:11.658 --> 03:26:18.637
MATT: That's a failure. That's a failure. And
