04:00:52.750 --> 04:00:54.055
TRAVIS: Yeah.

04:00:54.055 --> 04:00:55.874
LAURA: Yes, of course.

04:00:55.874 --> 04:00:57.124
MATT: (sighs) "Okay."

04:00:57.124 --> 04:00:58.874
TRAVIS: I say from outside the boat: Yeah.

04:00:58.874 --> 04:01:07.429
MATT: As you're walking alongside the boat, it's
going to pick up speed a little bit here. You're

04:01:07.429 --> 04:01:10.842
