04:01:12.188 --> 04:01:13.376
TRAVIS: I'll let it go.

04:01:13.376 --> 04:01:19.915
MATT: Okay. The mattress slides away and you see
water (spraying). It's a slow leak. It is still

04:01:19.915 --> 04:01:22.008
